<p-dialog
    [class]="modalClass"
    [(visible)]="displayGenericModal"
    [modal]="true"
    [closable]="false"
    [responsive]="true"
    (onAfterHide)="onClose()"
    [style]="{width: width, minWidth: '28rem'}"
    [minY]="70">
    <p-header>
        {{ title }}
    </p-header>
    <ng-content></ng-content>
    <p-footer>
        <button
            *ngIf="!hideCloseBtn"
            type="button"
            class=" button-with-neighbour"
            pButton
            (click)="onClose()"
            label="{{closeBtn}}"
            [ngClass]="closeBtnClass ? closeBtnClass:'ui-button-secondary'"
        >
        </button>
        <button
            *ngIf="!hideConfirmBtn"
            type="button"
            pButton
            (click)="onSubmit()"
            label="{{confirmBtn}}"
            [ngClass]="confirmBtnClass ? confirmBtnClass:'ui-button-primary'"
            [disabled]="disableConfirmBtn"
            >
        </button>
    </p-footer>
</p-dialog>

<p-panelMenu
  [model]="formattedItems"
  [multiple]="multiple"
  [style]="style"
  [styleClass]="styleClass"
  class="anef-ui-vmenu"
  [class.no-submenu]="isSingleLevel"
  [class.with-markers]="isWithMarkers"
  routerLinkActiveOptions="{exact: true}"
  ></p-panelMenu>

<p-tabView  orientation="left" class="anef-sidebar" [activeIndex]="activeIndex" (onChange)="handleChange($event)">
  <p-tabPanel leftIcon="{{ getIconClass(section.module) }}" *ngFor="let section of sections; let first = first;" [selected]="first">
    <ng-content *ngIf="section.module === SideBarType.DOCUMENTS" select="[documents]"></ng-content>
    <ng-content *ngIf="section.module === SideBarType.APPOINTMENT" select="[appointment]"></ng-content>
    <ng-content *ngIf="section.module === SideBarType.MESSAGESINTERN" select="[intern-messages]"></ng-content>
    <ng-content *ngIf="section.module === SideBarType.MESSAGES" select="[messages]"></ng-content>
    <ng-content *ngIf="section.module === SideBarType.HISTORIQUE" select="[historique]"></ng-content>
    <ng-content *ngIf="section.module === SideBarType.LIBRARY" select="[library]"></ng-content>
  </p-tabPanel>
</p-tabView>
